{"tid":2140400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟轟延選舉 促港府三思  斥DQ泛民候選人損國際聲譽","createTime":"2020-08-05T03:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T03:56:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91f90e2868a1158da634cc828378e7a72c2c0146","tid":2140400,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/HZPUHAALYEBMBU5LEV7WITGR3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FHZPUHAALYEBMBU5LEV7WITGR3Y%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=426f1cdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FHZPUHAALYEBMBU5LEV7WITGR3Y%2F&h=90a49006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/HZPUHAALYEBMBU5LEV7WITGR3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n歐盟轟延選舉 促港府三思 <br />\n斥DQ泛民候選人損國際聲譽<br />\n<br />\n歐盟前日發聲明，指香港延期舉行立法會選舉及撤銷多位反對派人士參選資格，令人質疑特區政府能否保障民主權利，並削弱香港自由開放的國際聲譽，呼籲香港當局重新考慮有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。除了延誤民主授權的更新外，亦惹人質疑《基本法》所保障的民主權利和自由能否行使。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/94P43h2ksXbkfYIgPhS8FLba5mw=/868x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4HEXLZF5ETRNEFIQZ3JOVNDSFE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F94P43h2ksXbkfYIgPhS8FLba5mw%3D%2F868x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4HEXLZF5ETRNEFIQZ3JOVNDSFE.gif&h=b9ec1621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐盟外交代表博雷利發聲明批評港府押後立法會選舉，籲重新考慮決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成員國陸續停引渡<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：憂國安法 居港台人部署撤離<br />\n<br />\n博雷利又提到港府近期撤銷多位泛民候選人參選資格，也削弱香港作為自由開放社會的國際聲譽，而保護香港的公民權利與政治權利是歐盟支持一國兩制的原則；他呼籲香港當局重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐歐盟使團發言人表示，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟早前曾因應中國強推港版國安法，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了德國和法國，英國、加拿大、新西蘭和澳洲都先後暫停予跟香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n中央社／24 Heures網站／中新社"},{"pid":"52057bb511c5ccc3e32c63689ff740d5c7bf900c","tid":2140400,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBbO6i2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBbO6i2.jpg&h=7f074337&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}